    "description": "【跳跃音符】可以绘制不同类型的板块，利用小球的碰撞创作随机的音乐。<br><br>通过一系列关卡的引导，你会逐渐掌握如何在&quot;画布&quot;上创造音乐。游戏中提供的物理轨迹预测功能，还可以辅助创作出美妙的音乐可视化作品。通过跳跃的小球，你可以从中看见音乐的韵律。<br><br>跳跃音符是一款实验游戏，尝试探讨视觉与音乐之间关系，更多新功能敬请期待：）<br><br><br>【玩法】<br>● 可听化   <br>有各种类型的板块可供玩家选择。你可以决定绘制板块的长度，板块越长，小球撞击板块时的音调越低。通过物理重力法则，你可以创作出独特的音乐。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/e84c4d4b12257846ab4413c11dcc0883.poster.avif?t=1670655138\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/e84c4d4b12257846ab4413c11dcc0883.webm?t=1670655138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/e84c4d4b12257846ab4413c11dcc0883.mp4?t=1670655138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.      <br><br>● 可视化<br>你无需是一位精通乐理的玩家才能创作出悦耳的音乐。通过游戏提供的 Midi 模式，你可以导入和使用各类经典的古典音乐作为你的创作素材。音乐信息会被自动转换为各类视觉元素，你可以设计小球的跳跃路径，轻松地创作出精彩的可视化动画。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/59254b65c4f8f4b5ce4a029d9f9ce1aa.poster.avif?t=1670655138\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/59254b65c4f8f4b5ce4a029d9f9ce1aa.webm?t=1670655138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/59254b65c4f8f4b5ce4a029d9f9ce1aa.mp4?t=1670655138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.      <br><br>● 关卡模式<br>这一模式会指导你如何创作音乐和动画，理解视觉和音乐之间微妙的关系。当你通过越多的关卡，你可以解锁更多的功能来丰富创作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/cf9d0fb31a6b24b6b765a593dd44018d.poster.avif?t=1670655138\" width=450 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/cf9d0fb31a6b24b6b765a593dd44018d.webm?t=1670655138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186730/extras/cf9d0fb31a6b24b6b765a593dd44018d.mp4?t=1670655138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.",
